#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Text number"</h2>
To use this software, you must provide your SMS texting number when you
create your account.  On creation, or if you change your SMS texting number
in the administration menu, a text will be sent to your SMS texting number
with confirmation instructions.
<p>Some functions will not work without a confirmed SMS texting number.
